        </span>
        <span class="brand-text">LUMENNYX STUDIOS</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
        <a href="/2257" class="active">2257 Notice</a>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-wrapper legal-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-logo-bg"></div>
      <h2>18 U.S.C. § 2257 Compliance Notice</h2>
      <p class="hero-note">
        Effective Date: <%= new Date().getFullYear() %><br>
        LumenNyx Studios – Wallkill, NY 12589
