        LumenNyx Studios were at least eighteen (18) years of age at the time of creation. The studio
        maintains government-issued photo identification and associated records for performers as required.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>2. Records Maintenance</h2>
      <p>
        LumenNyx Studios maintains age-verification and record-keeping documentation in accordance with
        applicable U.S. federal requirements, including 18 U.S.C. § 2257 and 28 C.F.R. Part 75, to the extent
        such requirements apply to the studio’s operations.
      </p>
      <p>
        Records are stored securely and are not intended to be publicly accessible. Access is restricted to
        authorized studio personnel and lawful compliance inquiries.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>3. Custodian of Records</h2>
      <p>
        The required records for all visual depictions created by LumenNyx Studios are maintained by the Designated
        Custodian of Records:
      </p>

