        LumenNyx Studios Records Administrator<br>
        Wallkill, NY 12589<br>
        Email:
        <a href="mailto:<%= email2257 %>"><%= email2257 %></a>
      </p>

      <p class="field-help">
        This contact information is for legal and compliance inquiries only.
        It is not for bookings or performer applications. For model onboarding, use
        <a href="mailto:<%= emailModels %>"><strong><%= emailModels %></strong></a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>4. Types of Content Covered</h2>
      <p>
        This notice applies to studio-created content involving actual sexually explicit conduct under federal law.
        Content that does not contain sexually explicit conduct as defined by 18 U.S.C. § 2256 is not subject to
        2257 requirements.
      </p>
      <p>This includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Studio-produced photo or video scenes</li>
        <li>BTS (behind-the-scenes) recordings involving explicit conduct</li>
        <li>Any content involving real performers in explicit acts</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>5. Third-Party Content</h2>
      <p>
        This studio does not host user-submitted content. All content on this website or private portal is produced
        directly by LumenNyx Studios with verified adult performers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>6. Portal vs. Public Content</h2>
      <p>
        The private model/staff portal itself is primarily for administrative and compliance operations and is not intended
        as a public distribution platform. The portal is used for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Identity verification</li>
        <li>Document upload</li>
        <li>Consent &amp; safety preferences</li>
        <li>Master release signatures</li>
        <li>Internal communication and scheduling</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>2257 compliance inquiries:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:<%= email2257 %>"><%= email2257 %></a><br>
        <strong>Legal notices:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:<%= emailLegal %>"><%= emailLegal %></a><br>
        <strong>General:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:<%= emailContact %>"><%= emailContact %></a>
